      "module_path": "track_resolution",
      "docs": "Secondary port for reading the current git branch name. Returns Some(\"HEAD\") for detached HEAD when the underlying GitRepository reports that sentinel, Some(branch_name) for named branches, and None only when no branch name can be determined. Infrastructure's SystemGitRepo implements this port. Declared in usecase (CN-04: usecase must not depend on infra; port inverts dependency). The current_branch return value is a raw Option<String> — the branch name is an opaque VCS string, not a validated domain concept at this boundary; callers (resolve_track_id_from_branch) apply the track/ validation on top, including mapping Some(\"HEAD\") to DetachedHead.",
